commit.title: Fix for bug #8848. I had inverted by mistake the update_evar_source
commit.message:
Fix for bug #8848. I had inverted by mistake the update_evar_source
function.

Instead of updating the undefined evar's info with the defined one it did
the converse... And check_evars was still using a check on the
evar_source while it should rather use the more abstract obligation_evar flag.
